title: Invisible Landscapes All Free Recordings [MP3 @ 320kbps]
description:
Invisible Landscapes is a Virginia Beach local band with many influences and ideas. They have a strong psychedelic rock influence with a touch of blues with some instrumental rock (post-rock) thrown in. These are mostly live recordings, so they're free! The others are self recorded with small recording devices. Hope you enjoy!

*Recommended for first time listeners
